reviewText: The dvds had several issues the package was wet, and nasty. The dvds didn't play.. Not just because they sent dvds that won't work in out players but upon closer look... They had very deep gashes in them.
This product doesnt work in any DVD player Ive ever tried. Ive tried multiple.
Did not know thus was for region 2 the USA is region 1 and bought these for my daughters 3rd birthday now I'm stuck with DVDs that can't be played
Doesn't even play in my player, not to mention I got it two months after the original shipping date.
These DVD's would not play on my DVD player.
It wouldn't play on my DVD player , it kept saying out of region! So I now have it to collect dust :(
